'''Jenet''' was the native [[Language/Legends|language]] of the [[Jenet/Legends|Jenet]] [[Species/Legends|species]] from [[Garban]]. Most Jenets were fluent in both the Jenet language and [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]]. The Jenet language was formed by squeaks, squeals and chatters, as well as high-pitched barks. Jenets relied only on oral tradition, and had no written version of their own language.<ref name="Ultimate Alien Anthology" />

